# Claude Code Configuration
# -------------------------
# If you're using project-level installation (symlink .claude directory),
# add this line to your project's .gitignore file:

.claude

# If you prefer to commit some project-specific configurations while
# ignoring others, you can be more selective:
#
# .claude/commands/
# .claude/agents/
# .claude/styles/
# !.claude/settings.local.json

# Note: This is not needed if you're using global installation,
# as the .claude directory won't exist in your project root.
